Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts13R.name: ResultClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts13R.abstract: The ResultClosure is used by other Codable aliases when responding with only a RequestError is needed

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts20C.name: CodableResultClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts20C.abstract: The CodableResultClosure is used by other Codable aliases when responding with an object which conforms to Codable or an RequestError is needed.

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts25C.name: CodableArrayResultClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts25C.abstract: The CodableArrayResultClosure is used by other Codable aliases when responding with an array of objects which conform to Codable or an RequestError is needed.

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts30I.name: IdentifierCodableResultClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts30I.abstract: The IdentifierCodableResultClosure is used by other Codable aliases when responding with an object which conforms to Codable and/or an obect that conforms to Identifier or RequestError is needed.

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts24I.name: IdentifierCodableClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts24I.abstract: The IdentifierCodableClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions utilising an object conforming to Identifier and an object conforming to ‘Codable’, then respond with an object which conforms to Codable, which is of the same type as the object passed as a parameter, or responding with a RequestError in the form of a CodableResultClosure

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts14C.name: CodableClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts14C.abstract: The CodableClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions utilising an object conforming to Identifier then respond with an object which conforms to Codable, which is of the same type as the object passed as a parameter, or responding with a RequestError in the form of a CodableResultClosure

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts24C.name: CodableIdentifierClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts24C.abstract: The CodableIdentifierClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions utilising an object conforming to Identifier, then respond with an object which conforms to Codable, and/or an object conforming to Identifier or responding with a RequestError in the form of a IdentifierCodableResultClosure

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts17N.name: NonCodableClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts17N.abstract: The NonCodableClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions then respond with a RequestError in the form of a ResultClosure

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts27I.name: IdentifierNonCodableClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts27I.abstract: The IdentifierNonCodableClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions utilising an object which conforms to Identifier then respond with a RequestError in the form of a ResultClosure

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts19C.name: CodableArrayClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts19C.abstract: The CodableArrayClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions then respond with an array of objects conforming to Codable or a RequestError in the form of a CodableArrayResultClosure

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts20S.name: SimpleCodableClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts20S.abstract: The SimpleCodableClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions then respond with an object conforming to Codable or a RequestError in the form of a CodableResultClosure.

Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts30I.name: IdentifierSimpleCodableClosure
Typealiases.html#/s:15KituraContracts30I.abstract: The IdentifierSimpleCodableClosure is for use in cases where you’d want to perform a series of actions utilising an object which conforms to Identifier then respond with an object conforming to Codable or a RequestError in the form of a CodableResultClosure
